{"tid":1922221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美股盤前三大指數期貨大跌超過5%再次觸發熔斷機制 所有交易暫停15分鐘！","createTime":"2020-03-12T12:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T13:37:27.000Z","uid":63113,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6b675bdd5161bda285172e4b887b242aab913d4c","tid":1922221,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0167aa4f5d2ad0ba7de4ea7fb93ff3688bbf9b9","tid":1922221,"uid":292710,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b675bdd5161bda285172e4b887b242aab913d4c","tid":1922221,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:26:45.000Z","msg":"又熔斷"},{"pid":"94083a33f31a2988f3d51dd90133715daf1176c8","tid":1922221,"uid":135961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:26:52.000Z","msg":"車厘"},{"pid":"ad6093bbee4b7fa21b8d8c90f0e43068690c314b","tid":1922221,"uid":63113,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:26:58.000Z","msg":"美股期貨指數再度跌到觸發熔斷機制！美股三大指數期貨下跌幅度再度達到5%，觸發芝加哥交易所的熔斷機制，暫停交易15分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n截至下午5點42分，標普500指數期貨下跌5.05%或138點。<br />\n<br />\n道瓊指數期貨下跌5.23%或1233點。<br />\n<br />\n那指期貨指數下跌5.05%或401點。<br />\n<br />\n美股的熔斷機制基準指數為標普500指數，一旦觸發，則美國所有股票、股價指數期貨與選擇權市場，都會跟著暫停交易。美股熔斷機制共分為3個階段，第一，當股價指數較前一個交易日下跌達7%時，股市將暫停交易15分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n第二，而當股價指數跌幅達13%時，股市將再度暫停交易15分鐘；第三，若當股價指數跌幅達20%時，股市將暫停交易至收盤為止。不過，若過了美東時間下午3時25分，除非跌幅達20%，否則即使跌逾7%、13%都不會暫停交易。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，美股盤前和盤後交易觸發暫停交易的跌幅比正規交易時間小，因此美股期指跌到5%即被暫停交易。<br />\n<br />\n全球股市陷入暴跌恐慌，亞股今日亦委靡不振，台股收盤下跌471點或4.33%，日股收盤下跌4.41%，韓股收盤下跌3.87%、港股收盤下跌3.66%，陸股則相對抗跌、收盤下跌1.52%<br />\n<br />\n另外，歐股今日早盤亦全線下挫，其中英國、法國、德國股市都一度下跌逾6%，目前跌幅則稍微收斂，來到6%以下。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php?news_id=1666222\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Famp%2Famp_news.php%3Fnews_id%3D1666222&d=xKwzLSQbN%2FgnQ4qVdIYE%2BAoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=ea6de802\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php?news_id=1666222</a>"},{"pid":"028d88e96f5ee6a2d1c039b91c758f54a832efef","tid":1922221,"uid":63113,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"94083a33f31a2988f3d51dd90133715daf1176c8","tid":1922221,"uid":135961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:26:52.000Z","msg":"車厘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q3rZF5M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ3rZF5M.png&h=3f6ea841&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f076bfe6bfbc01affb02fd847fa2e4adaa8de9fd","tid":1922221,"uid":71913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:29:44.000Z","msg":"夜期連止瀉藥都無"},{"pid":"60e496b8f83183752aa92a6af31b382bec03aada","tid":1922221,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:30:02.000Z","msg":"其實美股依幾日盡快跌仲好 <br />\n快速洗哂啲盤"},{"pid":"33b4190c20dc98400a03931c1f6d2b92ab7a98d9","tid":1922221,"uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:30:26.000Z","msg":"可能好快會谷底反彈<br />\n<br />\n美國加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488945aff2e728ea399ab0c52f8f703970c971d6","tid":1922221,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:30:38.000Z","msg":"呢D建議開去財經台"},{"pid":"ac68f0b4ac75fa733be1aea4da8a1b063a39ddce","tid":1922221,"uid":259010,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"028d88e96f5ee6a2d1c039b91c758f54a832efef","tid":1922221,"uid":63113,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"94083a33f31a2988f3d51dd90133715daf1176c8","tid":1922221,"uid":135961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:26:52.000Z","msg":"車厘"},"citedB